title: Cast of Power: Naturi Naughton and Joseph Sikora Interview and More
itunes:title: Cast of Power: Naturi Naughton and Joseph Sikora Interview and More
description:
Thursday 6/28 - Today on the show we were visited by some of the stars of the show Power,  Naturi Naughton and Joseph Sikora where they spoke about what we can expect in the new season, if Naturi is spiteful towards Spanish Women, Joseph once having anger problems and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Lakeith Standfield for giving a tired apology after posting an offensive video of him rapping about the LGBT community and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
